## Superseded from `standardize-matmul-calls`

```yaml
name: standardize-matmul-calls
description: 'Convert A.__matmul__(B) dunder method calls to matmul(A, B) function syntax.'
category: architecture
date: 2026-03-04
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Convert `A.__matmul__(B)` call sites to `matmul(A, B)`. Only convert call sites, not definitions
(`fn __matmul__`). Skip tests whose purpose is testing the dunder/operator directly.
Preserve operand order. Mojo-specific; matmul was already imported at affected call sites.

