TDD workflow for helper method extraction: write failing tests first, then implement.
`E2ERunner.__init__` wraps `tiers_dir` in `TierManager()` — always overwrite `runner.tier_manager`
directly after construction in unit tests. `runner.experiment_dir` starts as `None` — set
