## Superseded from `dry-mojo-test-helper-extraction`

```yaml
name: dry-mojo-test-helper-extraction
description: 'Extract duplicated Mojo test tensor setup into a private helper returning a tuple.'
category: architecture
date: 2026-03-15
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Extract identical tensor construction blocks into `_make_test_<op>_tensors()` private helper.
Mojo v0.26.x does NOT support tuple destructuring in `var` declarations — use indexed access
`tensors[0]`, `tensors[1]`. Helper must appear before first caller (definition-before-use).
Verified ProjectOdyssey Issue #3870: -10 net lines, identical behavior, test count unchanged.

