## Superseded from `extract-method-refactoring`

```yaml
name: extract-method-refactoring
description: 'Decompose large methods and inline closures into focused helper methods.'
category: architecture
date: 2026-01-01
version: 2.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Extract one method at a time and verify before proceeding. Naming: `_action_exp_<state>`,
`_action_tier_<state>`. Closures with `nonlocal` → mutable box pattern (`list[T | None]`).
Critical: assert mocks INSIDE the `with patch.object(...)` block, not after. Ruff D401:
reword docstrings to imperative mood. Verified ProjectScylla PR #709: 90 LOC → 30 LOC,
2145 tests passing.

