## Superseded from `deprecated-file-stub-cleanup`

```yaml
name: deprecated-file-stub-cleanup
description: "Safely delete deprecated files and stubs."
category: tooling
date: 2026-03-28
version: "1.0.0"
user-invocable: false
verification: unverified
```

Safe-to-delete stub: zero executable code, zero exports. Always grep ALL file types including
`.md`, `.yaml`, `scripts/*.py` (agent config generators). For Mojo stubs: directory with
`__init__.mojo` at same level means stub is shadowed and unused. Skip `mojo-format` hook with
`SKIP=mojo-format` when GLIBC mismatch prevents local Mojo build. Always check `git status`
and `gh pr list` first — prior automation may have already completed the work.
Verified on 4 ProjectOdyssey issues: #3062, #3063, #3066, and `schedulers.mojo` stub cleanup.

